high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the round white table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the butter knife that is closest to the paper towel roll on the table.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the wall, turn left again to face the round white table.
Slice up the loaf of bread that is on the table.
Put the butter knife you are holding down on the table to the right of the white plate.
Pick the end slice of bread off of the white table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the black fridge.
Open the door and place the slice of bread inside, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled slice of bread, then close the door.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the small silver bin on the ground next to the counter.
Put the chilled slice of bread into the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in a silver bin.

high_descs: turn around, go to white dining table to the right
pick up silver knife from behind white container on table
go around table to the side with white plate and salt shaker
slice bread on table
place knife perpendicularly on knife to the right of the plate
pick up slice of bread from table
turn around, go to refrigerator on the right
open refrigerator, place bread slice to the left of bowl on top shelf, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up slice of bread from top shelf, close refrigerator
turn to right, go to end of counter with silver bin
place bread slice in silver bin
anns.task_desc: Place chilled bread slice in silver bin

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table in front of the window.
Pick up the knife behind the paper towels on the table.
Walk to the right side of the table.
Cut the loaf of bread on the table.
Place the knife on top of the knife to the right of the plate on the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge in the opposite corner of the room.
Chill the piece of bread in the fridge and then pick the piece of bread up from the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the gray trash can at the end of the counter on your left.
Place the piece of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of bread into the gray trash can.
